

Market
has:
  a HashMap (books) of instrument_id's that indexes a vector of (Publisher,Book) entries

Book
has:
  a HashMap (orders_by_id) of order id's that indexes a (Side, i64) tuple
  a BtreeMap (offers) that has price levels that index a Level
  a BtreeMap (bids) that has price levels that index a Level

Level
  is just a type that specifies a VecDeque<MboMsg>


PriceLevel
has:
  price - the level's price
  count - ??
  size - total number of shares






Mbo "Action" field
Add - Insert a new order into the book
Modify - Change an order's price and/or size
Cancel - Fully or partially cancel an order from the book
Clear - Remove all resting orders for the instrument
Trade - An aggressing order traded. Does not affect the book
Fill - resting order was filled. Does not affect the book
None - no action but may carry flags or other information




